<COREF ID="30260" TYPE="IDENT">A large scale clearing away of silt from <COREF ID="30288" TYPE="IDENT">the Kunming Lake in <COREF ID="30264" TYPE="IDENT">the Summer Palace</COREF></COREF> , which was the first time in the 240 years since <COREF ID="30288" TYPE="IDENT">the lake</COREF> came into being ,</COREF> began late last year .
